      "content": "hey, i'm running into a major MemoryError in my python script. im using pandas to process some massive csv files but as soon as the loop hits the halfway point, the whole thing just crashes. i was thinking about switching from list comprehensions to generator functions to save some space? would that actually help with the overhead or is there something else i should be looking at?",
